text: Sonya Singha (; born April 8, 1994) is a Thai actress, singer, and host. ==Career== Kat was in a duo with Patt Piraya. She was also a host to KamiKaze Channel. She was under Kamikaze company from 2010 to 2013. In 2013, she signed a contract with Channel 7. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Thai actors Category:Living people Category:Thai singers
title: Sonya Singha
